                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Entry Card 5 -->
            <div class="entry-card">
                <div class="entry-header">
                    <div class="entry-date">
                        <span class="date-day">17</span>
                        <span class="date-month">Dec</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="entry-info">
                        <h3 class="entry-title">Challenging Tuesday</h3>
                        <div class="entry-meta">
                            <span class="meta-item">Tuesday, December 17, 2025</span>
                            <span class="meta-dot">•</span>
                            <span class="meta-item">10:15 PM</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="entry-mood">
                        <span class="mood-badge mood-anxious">Anxious</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="entry-content">
                    <p class="entry-excerpt">
                        Had a tough day at work with several unexpected challenges. Feeling a bit overwhelmed but trying to stay positive.
                        Reminding myself that difficult days are temporary and tomorrow is a new opportunity...
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="entry-footer">
                    <div class="entry-tags">
